<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Proteção de dados</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-giJF6kkoqNQ00vy+HMDP7azOuL0xtbfIcaT9wjKHr8RbDVddVHyTfAAsrekwKmP1"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/style.css">
  <body class="bg-light">
    <header class="bg-dark text-light text-center py-4">
      <h1>Data Protection Law Around the World</h1>
      <p>
        Here you can find information about data protection law in diferent
        countries and regions. You can also find links to help you get deeper
        information
      </p>
      <form method="get" action="/">
        <select
          name="country"
          id="country"
          class="form-select w-25 mx-auto"
          onchange="this.form.submit()"
        >
          <option value="">Select a country/region</option>
          <option value="BR">Brazil</option>
          <option value="EU">Europe</option>
          <option value="EUA">United States</option>
        </select>
      </form>
    </header>
  </body>
</html>
